title: "MRMS Cookbook"
abstract: "The Multi-Radar, Multi-Sensor (MRMS) project combines radar data, surface observations, and numerical weather prediction models to create near real-time composites of radar fields and precipitation. In this cookbook, we demonstrate how to access and visualize historical and real-time MRMS data."
